#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:70
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Gray Scale Test Image"
msgid "Grey Scale Test Image"
msgstr "Testbillede med gråskala"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "You should be able to see the following:"
msgstr "Du skal kunne se følgende:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "A gray scale with 20 different sections"
msgid "A grayscale with 20 different sections"
msgstr "En gråskala med 20 forskellige dele"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "The darkest section pure black"
msgstr "Den mørkeste del er fuldstændig sort"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "The lightest section pure white"
msgstr "Den lyseste del er fuldstændig hvid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "No hint of any color in the gray tones"
msgstr "Ingen farve i de grå farvetoner"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you can't see all of the 20 sections, use your monitors contrast "
#| "settings or the \"Gamma\" slider of &kgamma; to correct this. If black is "
#| "not pure black, try to darken the monitor, if white is not pure white, "
#| "try to lighten it. If you see any colors in the gray tones alter the "
#| "color balance settings of your monitor or the \"Red\", \"Green\" and "
#| "\"Blue\" slider of &kgamma;."
msgid ""
"If you cannot see all of the 20 sections, use your monitors contrast "
"settings or the <guilabel>Gamma:</guilabel> slider to correct this. If black "
"is not pure black, try to darken the monitor, if white is not pure white, "
"try to lighten it. If you see any colors in the gray tones alter the color "
"balance settings of your monitor or the <guilabel>Red:</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Green:</guilabel> and <guilabel>Blue:</guilabel> sliders."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du ikke kan se alle 20 dele, så brug billeddskærmens "
"kontrastindstilling eller skyderen \"Gamma\" i &kgamma; til at korrigere "
"det. Hvis sort ikke er rigtigt sort, forsøg at gøre skærmen mørkere. Hvis "
"hvidt ikke er rigtigt hvidt, forsøg at gøre den lysere. Hvis du ser nogle "
"farver i de grå toner, ændr skærmens farvebalance eller skyderen \"Rød\", "
"\"Grøn\" eller \"Blå\" i &kgamma;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:95
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "RGB Scale Test Image"
msgid "RGB Scale Test Picture"
msgstr "Testbillede med RGB-skala"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You should be able to see three strips, each with 16 sections of red, green "
"or blue tones. The darkest sections should be pure black, the brightest "
"should be pure red, green or blue. If you don't see all sections of a color "
"strip, try to lighten or darken this color."
msgstr ""
"Du skal kunne se tre linjer, hver med 16 dele af røde , grønne eller blå "
"toner. De mørkeste dele skal være rent sorte, og de lyseste rent røde, "
"grønne eller blå. Hvis du ikke ser alle delene i en farvelinje, så forsøg at "
"gøre farven lysere eller mørkere."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:104
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "CMY Scale Test Image"
msgid "CMY Scale Test Picture"
msgstr "Testbillede med CMY-skala"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You should be able to see three strips, each with 11 sections of cyan, "
"magenta or yellow tones. The brightest sections should be pure white, the "
"darkest should be pure cyan, magenta or yellow."
msgstr ""
"Du skal kunne se alle tre linjer, hver med 11 dele turkise, magenta eller "
"gule toner. De lyseste dele skal være rent hvide, og de mørkeste skal være "
"ren turkis, magenta eller gul."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "If you can't see all cyan sections, try to lighten or darken red"
msgid "If you cannot see all cyan sections, try to lighten or darken red"
msgstr ""
"Hvis du ikke kan se alle de turkise dele, så forsøg at gøre rødt lysere "
"eller mørkere"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:115
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you can't see all magenta sections, try to lighten or darken green"
msgid "If you cannot see all magenta sections, try to lighten or darken green"
msgstr ""
"Hvis du ikke kan se alle de magenta dele, så forsøg at gøre grønt lysere "
"eller mørkere"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "If you can't see all yellow sections, try to lighten or darken blue"
msgid "If you cannot see all yellow sections, try to lighten or darken blue"
msgstr ""
"Hvis du ikke kan se alle de gule dele, så forsøg at gøre blåt lysere eller "
"mørkere"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:124
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Advanced Test Images"
msgid "Advanced Test Pictures"
msgstr "Avancerede testbilleder"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The following three pictures shows you the abilities of your monitor at "
#| "three points of the gray spectrum. If you can't see all of the details, "
#| "don't be worry, or buy better hardware."
msgid ""
"The following three pictures show you the abilities of your monitor at three "
"points of the gray spectrum. If you cannot see all of the details, don't be "
"worry, or buy better hardware."
msgstr ""
"Følgende tre billeder viser hvad billedskærmen kan klare på tre punkter i "
"gråskalaen. Hvis du ikke kan se alle detaljer, skal det ikke bekymre dig, "
"eller købe en bedre skærm."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:131
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Dark Gray Test Image"
msgid "Dark Gray Test Picture"
msgstr "Mørkegrå testbillede"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You should be able to see 10 different rectangles of dark gray within a "
"black box. The chart shows you 1% steps from black."
msgstr ""
"Du skal kunne se ti forskellige mørkegrå rektangler i et sort felt. "
"Diagrammet viser trin i 1% fra sort."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:138
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Mid Gray Test Image"
msgid "Mid Gray Test Picture"
msgstr "Middelgrå testbillede"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This picture shows you 11 gray rectangles within a 50% gray box. You should "
"be able to see all of the rectangles except the middle one. The rectangles "
"represent the steps from 45% to 55% gray."
msgstr ""
"Dette billede viser 11 grå rektangler i et 50% gråt felt. Du skal kunne se "
"alle rektanglerne undtagen den i midten. Rektanglerne viser trin fra 45 % "
"til 55 % gråt."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:146
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Light Gray Test Image"
msgid "Light Gray Test Picture"
msgstr "Lysegrå testbillede"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You should be able to see 10 different rectangles of light gray within a "
"white box. The chart shows you 1% steps from white."
msgstr ""
"Du skal kunne se ti forskellige lysegrå rektangler i et hvidt felt. "
"Diagrammet viser trin i 1% fra hvidt."

